    "deviceClass": "Class II",
    "hasApplicabilityConstraint": {
      "description": "Model is applicable to centrifugal blood pumps operating within the CPB flow regime (2–7 L/min), at rotational speeds of 1500–3500 RPM, with blood viscosity in the range 2.7–4.0 mPa·s. Applicability is restricted to devices geometrically similar to the FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark within ±15% dimensional tolerance.",
